C Y B E R W A R E

Porter droid
Usage: droid


     The porter droid is a small robotic unit that follows you.
It is like a bag, in that you can place or remove items from
it.  The droid offers safe transportation of your items.  If you
and your droid are somehow separated, your droid will find you. 
Your quality level will reflect the droid's quality.
The droid will also make trades for you.

